The problem is that you cannot modify people&#x27;s behaviour by pointing them to something existing:<p>harry: &quot;hey, utc would be great, let&#x27;s drop CEST.&quot;
joana: &quot;UTC was designed for something else ... <more offtopic arguments&quot;<p>whereas with SUT, you have the chance to change behaviour:<p>harry: &quot;There&#x27;s a new time format, SUT. If we adapt to it, the world will become much simpler.&quot;
joana: &quot;Wow, so cool. Let&#x27;s do that!&quot;
